---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
    title="Childcare Communication Apps | Childcare Business Plan"
    description="Evaluate childcare communication apps based on staff adoption and parent expectations, not just features."
>
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-16 px-4">
        <!-- 1. OWNERSHIP FRAMING -->
        <section class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                YOUR parent communication
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
                Great communication isn't about which app you use—it's about
                building trust and transparency with the families you serve.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. FACTORS THAT AFFECT OUTCOME -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                What Affects App Success
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                The success of any communication tool depends entirely on your
                staff's willingness to adopt it and your parents' expectations
                for updates. A feature-rich app is useless if your team finds it
                too cumbersome to use during a busy day.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. WHY GENERIC ADVICE FAILS -->
        <section class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
                Why Online Advice Often Conflicts
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
                Tech reviews often focus on feature lists rather than real-world
                usability in a childcare setting. Your choice should be driven
                by your specific workflow and the level of engagement your
                parents actually want, not what a software salesperson says you
                need.
            </p>
        </section>

        <!-- 4. CTA TO CALCULATOR -->
        <section
            class="text-center py-12 px-8 glass-panel rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm bg-white/50 backdrop-blur-sm"
        >
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
                See How Much YOU Could Make in Your State
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
                Get your personalized income estimate based on your state's
                regulations to see how technology investment impacts your bottom
                line.
            </p>
            <a
                href="/tools/income-builder"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-teal-600 hover:bg-teal-700 text-white font-medium px-8 py-4 shadow-lg transition-all"
            >
                Use the Free Calculator →
            </a>
        </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
